data.title: Watering Hole from the 70's
data.text: The only two things good about this bar is the Beer is cold.And the Bikers are like Family...                                                                                                                           P.S. Bring your own Air freshener.Because there is a lot of gas passing going on in side...          P.P.S. Be careful when Lighting up.

data.title: Your Typical Dive Bar
data.text: Nothing terrible here, truly. It's a typical dive bar with cold beer, efficient staff & some crazy (yet oddly cool) drunks sitting around the bar.

data.title: Palm Bay's version of Cheers!
data.text: Local beer and wine pub. Friendly people. Live music on weekends outside.  Horseshoe tournaments.  Pool table.  It is a very old place but a great little watering hole

data.title: Ok for a beer
data.text:
Small local bar near US-1 ...stopped in for a beer due to curiosity.  Good place for Palm Bay's new Friday Fest on the 1st Friday of the month.  
Not a place for dining or romantic evenings...fine for a couple of drinks tho.
